      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $ABCDEFG$ un heptagone (7 côtés) plan régulier. On pose\n$\\alpha = AB$, $\\beta = AC$, $\\gamma = AD$ (distances).\n\nMontrer que $\\frac 1\\alpha = \\frac 1\\beta + \\frac 1\\gamma$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(ABCDEFG\\)</span> un heptagone (7 côtés) plan régulier. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha = AB\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\beta = AC\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\gamma = AD\\)</span> (distances).</p>\n<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac 1\\alpha = \\frac 1\\beta + \\frac 1\\gamma\\)</span>.</p>\n"
